---
title: Honey-Glazed Halloumi & Pearl Couscous with Roast Veggies & Basil Pesto
description: Indulge your taste buds with a tantalizing dish of honey-glazed halloumi nestled atop a bed of fluffy couscous and perfectly roasted veggies. The vibrant flavours are elevated with the addition of basil pesto, creating a harmonious and satisfying culinary experience.
